---
layout: layouts/base.njk
---
<header class="content framed">
  <h1>Hello there! 👋🏼</h1>
  <p>Welcome to a demo of <code>terminus</code>, a minimal dark theme for static sites.</p>
  <p>This port preserves the original design direction and content model using Eleventy.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/panr/hugo-theme-terminal">panr/hugo-theme-terminal</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/ejmg/zerm">ejmg/zerm</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/welpo/tabi">welpo/tabi</a></li>
  </ul>
</header>

{% from "macros/post.njk" import postExcerpt %}
{% set maxPosts = site.homeMaxPosts or 3 %}

{% for post in collections.posts %}
  {% if loop.index <= maxPosts %}
    {{ postExcerpt(post) }}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if (collections.posts | length) > maxPosts %}
<nav class="pagination">
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/blog/" aria-label="all posts">[all posts]&nbsp;&gt;</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>
{% endif %}
